sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Jupyter as JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGINX as NGINX Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CodeSrv as code-server<br/>8787/TCP HTTP
    participant Elyra as Elyra Pipeline<br/>Editor
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>API
    participant Runtime as Runtime Image<br/>Pod

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accesses JupyterLab Workbench

    User->>Gateway: GET https://workbench.apps.cluster/<br/>Auth: OIDC/OAuth
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>8443/TCP TLS<br/>Bearer Token
    RBAC->>RBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(validates user access)
    RBAC->>Jupyter: Forward to upstream<br/>8888/TCP HTTP (pod-local)
    Jupyter-->>RBAC: JupyterLab UI response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>User: HTML/JS JupyterLab UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1b: Notebook uses oc CLI

    Jupyter->>K8sAPI: oc get pods / kubectl commands<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Jupyter: API response

    Note over User,CodeSrv: Flow 2: User Accesses Code Server Workbench

    User->>Gateway: GET https://codeserver.apps.cluster/<br/>Auth: OIDC/OAuth
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>8443/TCP TLS<br/>Bearer Token
    RBAC->>NGINX: Forward to upstream<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (pod-local)
    NGINX->>CodeSrv: Reverse proxy<br/>8787/TCP HTTP
    CodeSrv-->>NGINX: VS Code UI response
    NGINX-->>RBAC: HTTP response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>User: HTML/JS VS Code UI

    Note over User,Runtime: Flow 3: Pipeline Runtime Execution

    Elyra->>KFP: Submit pipeline<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KFP->>Runtime: Launch runtime image pod<br/>via Kubernetes API<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute pipeline node code<br/>(headless, no IDE)
    Runtime-->>KFP: Execution complete<br/>(exit code + artifacts)
